  <center>
    <h3>Monthly singings</h3>
  </center>

  <p>(A) Goshen, Indiana: First Sundays, 4:00-6:00 pm, followed by
  potluck
  supper. <a
  href='http://maps.google.com/maps?q=407+N.+First+St.+Goshen,+IN&amp;hl=en'
  target='new'>Lind residence, 407 N. First St,</a>, Contact person:
  <a href="http://homepage.mac.com/mlind/Menu8.html">Matthew Lind</a>,
  574-533-8259, or Samuel Sommers, 574-294-6180, scmws -at-
  yahoo.com</p>

  <p>(B) Ann Arbor, Michigan: Second Sundays, 2:00-5:00 pm, <a href=
  'http://maps.google.com/maps?q=316+S+Main+St,+Ann+Arbor,+MI+48104&amp;iwloc=A&amp;hl=en'
  target='new'>The Ark Coffeehouse, 316 South Main</a>, Ann Arbor.
  Contact person: Charlotte Wolfe, cawolfe -at- umich.edu or The
  Ark, 734-761-1800</p>

 <p>(C) Howard County, Indiana: Second Sundays, 2:00-5:00
  pm, <a
  href="http://local.google.com/local?f=q&hl=en&q=4903+N+200+E,+Kokomo,+IN+46901&ll=40.548057,-86.08969&spn=0.326095,0.587082"
  target='new'>Bahler residence, 4903 N. County Road 200 E.</a>,
  Howard Country, near Kokomo, Indiana.  Contact person: Brad Baher,
  bahler1 -at- netzero.net, 765-457-9159 </p>

  <p>(D) Kalamazoo: Third Sundays, 4:00-6:00 pm followed by potluck
  supper, and preceded (at 3:00 pm) by Christian Harmony and "other book" singing <a href=
  "http://maps.google.com/maps?q=529+Pinehurst+Blvd,+Kalamazoo,+MI&amp;hl=en">
  529 Pinehurst Blvd.</a>, Bill &amp; Martha Beverly, 269-382-4288,
  mbeverly -at- chartermi.net</p>


  <p>(E) East Lansing: 1st and 3rd Tuesdays, 7-9pm. Location: <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=469+N.+Hagadorn+Road,+East+Lansing&sll=37.0625,-95.677068&sspn=48.374125,59.853516&ie=UTF8&z=16">Edgewood United Church of Christ, 469 N. Hagadorn</a>.
    Contact persons: Bob Borcherding, singing -at- fasolamichigan.org, <a href="http://fasolamichigan.org">fasolamichigan.org</a>

  <center>
    <h3>Annual singings</h3>
  </center>

  <p>Saturday before the third Sunday in July: Michiana All-day
  Singing, New Testament Baptist Church, <a href=
  "http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=24899+C.R.+40,+Goshen+IN&sll=41.553811,-85.896606&sspn=0.598109,1.146698&ie=UTF8&z=16&iwloc=A">
  rural Goshen area</a>. Contact person: Samuel Sommers,
  574-294-6180, scmws -at- yahoo.com</p>

  <p>Third Sunday in July: Kalamazoo All-day Singing, <a href=
  "http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2101+Wilbur+Ave,+Kalamazoo,+MI&amp;hl=en">
  Wesley Foundation</a> at Western Michigan University. Contact
  persons: Bill and Martha Beverly, 269-382-4288, mbeverly -at-
  chartermi.net</p>

  <p>Also: New Years Day Harmonia Sacra Singing, Associated Mennonite Biblical Seminary, <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=3003+Benham+Avenue,+Elkhart,+IN&amp;hl=en">3003 Benham Avenue</a>, Elkhart, Indiana, New Year's Day, 1 - 5pm EST, Potluck supper to follow</p>

